{
  "id": "adv_card_szk_03_01_short",
  "title": "兵藤雫 (Short)",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "living-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "雫、この間話したソロデビューの件、考えてくれたか？",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんなさい……\nやっぱりソロは無理……自信、無い……",
      "startTime": 7.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "でも歌うのは好き……\n{user}さんの期待にも応えたい……",
      "startTime": 16.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "それで考えた……一人じゃなければ……\n一緒に歌ってくれる人がいたら出来る……かも……",
      "startTime": 25.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ツインボーカルか……雫自身の気持ちも大事だしな\n誰か一緒にやりたい相手はいるのか？",
      "startTime": 35.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "……天動瑠依さん",
      "startTime": 38.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "天動さん？\n意外だな、てっきりサニピか月ストの誰かかと……",
      "startTime": 41.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメ？",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_03_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、ダメじゃないよ\nただ天動さんが引き受けてくれるかどうか……",
      "startTime": 50.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}